Uses of Interface
org.soulwing.cdi.properties.spi.PropertyResolver

  • Packages that use PropertyResolver 
    Package Description
    org.soulwing.cdi.properties.resolvers
    Built-in property resolvers

    • Uses of PropertyResolver in org.soulwing.cdi.properties.resolvers

      Classes in org.soulwing.cdi.properties.resolvers that implement PropertyResolver 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  AbstractPackagePathPropertyResolver
      An abstract base for PropertyResolvers that treat property names as a qualified path name to a properties resource.
      class  ClassPathBeanPropertiesResolver
      A PropertyResolver that resolves values by considering each property name to be a path to a beans.properties resource on the class path.
      class  JndiEnvBeanPropertiesResolver
      A resolver that looks up a JNDI environment variable and (if found) interprets it as a space and/or comma delimited list of URLs to properties files to consult (in the given order) for name resolution.
      class  JndiEnvUrlPathBeanPropertiesResolver
      A resolver that looks up a JNDI environment variable and (if found) interprets it as a space and/or comma delimited list of URLs to properties files to consult (in the given order) for name resolution.
      class  MetaInfBeanPropertiesResolver
      A resolver that looks for META-INF/beans.properties resources on the classpath and uses all such properties resources to attempt to resolve bean properties.
      class  SystemPropertiesResolver
      A PropertyResolver that consults system properties.
      class  SystemPropertyFileResolver
      A PropertyResolver that loads a property file referenced by a System property.
      class  UrlPathBeanPropertiesResolver
      A PropertyResolver that resolves values by considering each property name to be a path to a beans.properties resource on the class path.
